# Complete Fix for Host Dashboard

## Problem:
The host dashboard was falling back to customer dashboard because of:
1. Incorrect user validation using `JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('user') || '{}')` - empty object {} is truthy
2. Code that was setting a default demo user that was overwriting actual user sessions

## Quick Fix - Clear Browser Storage:
If you're logged in with wrong data, visit:
http://localhost:3000/clear-storage.html
Click "Clear All Data" button to reset.

Then:
1. Go to http://localhost:3000/index.html (Welcome page)
2. Click Login or Sign Up
3. After login, you'll be redirected to the correct dashboard based on your role

## Detailed Fix - Code Changes:

### FIX 1: In host-dashboard.html - Authentication Check (around line 370)
Replace:
```javascript
// Initialize dashboard when DOM is loaded
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
  const isLoggedIn = localStorage.getItem('isLoggedIn');
  const user = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('user') || '{}');
  if (!isLoggedIn) {
    window.location.href = 'login-signup.html';
    return;
  }
  if (user.role === 'customer') {
    window.location.href = 'customer-dashboard.html';
    return;
  }
  if (user.role === 'admin') {
    window.location.href = 'admin-dashboard.html';
    return;
  }
  if (user.role !== 'host') {
    window.location.href = 'login-signup.html';
    return;
  }
  initializeHostDashboard();
});
```

With:
```javascript
// Initialize dashboard when DOM is loaded
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
  // Properly validate user authentication with try-catch
  let user = null;
  try {
    const userStr = localStorage.getItem('user');
    user = userStr ? JSON.parse(userStr) : null;
  } catch (e) {
    console.error('Error parsing user data:', e);
    user = null;
  }
  
  const isLoggedIn = localStorage.getItem('isLoggedIn');
  
  // Check if not logged in or no valid user with role
  if (!isLoggedIn || !user || !user.role) {
    console.log('Not logged in or invalid user, redirecting to login');
    window.location.href = 'login-signup.html';
    return;
  }
  
  // Role-based redirect - ensure host stays on host dashboard
  if (user.role === 'customer') {
    console.log('User is a customer, redirecting to customer dashboard');
    window.location.href = 'customer-dashboard.html';
    return;
  }
  if (user.role === 'admin') {
    console.log('User is an admin, redirecting to admin dashboard');
    window.location.href = 'admin-dashboard.html';
    return;
  }
  if (user.role !== 'host') {
    console.log('User role is not host:', user.role);
    window.location.href = 'login-signup.html';
    return;
  }
  
  // User is confirmed as host - initialize dashboard
  console.log('User authenticated as host, initializing dashboard');
  initializeHostDashboard();
});
```

